      <ul>
        <li>Opening business bank accounts</li>
        <li>Applying for business licenses</li>
        <li>Tax filings</li>
        <li>Insurance applications</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Obtain an EIN (Employer Identification Number) from the IRS</li>
        <li>Open a business bank account</li>
        <li>Apply for any required business licenses</li>
        <li>Set up business accounting</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing Corppy! If you need any additional services, feel free to reach out.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
